# 💬 ChatNav — Smart Chat Application

A full stack chat application built to solve real problems faced in WhatsApp daily.

---

## 🚀 About The Project

ChatNav is a full stack chat application developed using Core Java, JDBC, MySQL, HTML, CSS and JavaScript. This project was built by identifying real problems faced in WhatsApp and providing better solutions.

---

## ❌ Problems I Identified in WhatsApp

- Search option is hidden behind 3 dots — most users don't even know it exists
- Cannot search messages by typing date manually — only calendar selection works
- No scrollbar inside chats — have to scroll manually with hand
- When starred message is deleted — screen automatically jumps down
- WhatsApp does not show "No messages found" — jumps to nearest message instead
- Have to switch between 3 different apps for Chat, Notes and Todo

---

## ✅ Solutions I Built in ChatNav

- Search bar directly visible inside every chat
- Search by text, image, video, audio, PDF type
- Search by year only, month/year, or full date DD/MM/YYYY
- Matching text highlights in yellow like Ctrl+F
- Scrollbar inside every chat window
- Scroll position stays fixed when message is deleted
- Clearly shows "No images found" or "No messages found on this date"
- Notes section built inside the app — add, edit, search, delete
- Todo list built inside the app — add tasks with reminder alert
- Pending and Completed tasks shown separately
- Media section shows all images, videos, audios, documents separately
- Forward message to any contact
- Starred messages section inside each chat

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Backend | Core Java, JDBC |
| Database | MySQL |
| Frontend | HTML, CSS, JavaScript |
| Storage | localStorage |

