## ✨ Features

- 💬 Real time chat with auto replies
- 🔍 Smart search with text highlighting
- 📅 Flexible date search — year, month/year, full date
- 📁 Send images, videos, audios, PDFs, documents
- ⭐ Star important messages
- 🗑️ Delete messages with fixed scroll position
- 📂 Media section — images, videos, audios, docs separately
- ➤ Forward messages to any contact
- 📝 Notes — add, edit, search, delete
- ✅ Todo list with reminder bell alert
- 💾 All data saved permanently in localStorage and MySQL

---

## 🎯 Key Highlights

- Identified real world problems in existing chat platforms
- Built end to end full stack solution from scratch
- Complete CRUD operations with MySQL database
- Persistent data storage across sessions
- Clean and modern dark themed UI

